是多项运动的庞然大物。&lt;/em>; |插图由 Will Joel / The Verge 绘制&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;Garmin 可能以其硬核健身手表而闻名，但它也提供广泛的生活方式产品。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23691498/best-garmin-smartwatch-fitness-tracker-wearables&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23691498/best-garmin-smartwatch-fitness-tracker-wearables" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23691498/best-garmin-smartwatch-fitness-tracker-wearables</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-04-01T09:44:32-04:00</published><updated> 2024-04-01T09:44:32-04:00</updated><title>随着反垄断压力的加大，微软将 Teams 从 Office 中剥离出来</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Microsoft Teams 徽标的矢量插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/pUw5jRH3mqylqJy4PYpd9RzBD-g=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73246598/STK264_MICROSOFT_TEAMS_V2_CVIRGINIA _B.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;j3bPZN&quot;>;微软可能希望转移欧盟正在进行的反垄断调查的打击，正在将 Teams 从 Office 365 剥离到作为自己的独立应用程序在全球销售，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.reuters.com/technology/microsoft-separate-teams-office-globally-amid-antitrust-scrutiny-2024-04-01/&quot;>;&lt; em>;路透社今天报道&lt;/a>;。一位公司发言人告诉&lt;em>;路透社&lt;/em>;，在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://blogs.microsoft.com/eupolicy/ 2023/08/31/european-competition-teams-office-microsoft-365/&quot;>;去年已经在欧盟这样做了&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;m61hXU&quot;>;微软的现有客户应该是能够保留当前的优惠（将 Teams 与 Office 和其他产品捆绑在一起）、续订、更新或选择新优惠。对于新注册的人来说，Teams 本身的价格为 5.25 美元，而没有 Teams 的 Office 套餐的价格为 7.75 美元到 54.75 美元。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;6PRbSE&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Microsoft 正在欧洲将 Teams 从 Office 中分拆，以解决监管机构的担忧&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/31/23853517/microsoft- team-unbundling-europe&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;qrtssS&quot;>;去年 8 月，微软首次在欧盟剥离了 Teams，...&lt;/ p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/1/24117785/microsoft-teams-office-split-eu-regulation-antitrust-investigation&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/一个>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/1/24117785/microsoft-teams-office-split-eu-regulation-antitrust-investigation" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/4/1/24117785/microsoft-teams-office-split-eu-regulation-antitrust-investigation</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-04-01T08:05:03-04:00</published><updated> 2024-04-01T08:05:03-04:00</updated><title> Gmail 20 周年</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一个人皱着眉头被电子邮件包围的像素插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/G9FI3Ogh4Go2dRmOuwTM5V7wfE8=/0x0:1750x1167/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73241540/247048_Gmail_20_Years_1750_NLi ttle.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Nick Little 为 The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;Gmail 凭借快速搜索和 1GB 存储空间彻底改变了电子邮件。但接下来会走向何方？&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24113616/gmail-email-20-years-old-internet&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24113616/gmail-email-20-years-old-internet" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24113616/gmail-email-20-years-old-internet</id><author><name>宋茜</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-03-31T10:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-03-31T10:00:00-04:00</updated><title>塞尔达传说背后的团队如何让物理感觉像魔法</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/i1TYhb7ZcVSoiODw4XgqNWnA_Yc=/0x0:1351x901/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73245135 /Tears_of_the_Kingdom_Press_Image.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：任天堂&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/fi